{"tid":2412762,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"冚家 GME　冇銀用就要 strong hold","createTime":"2021-02-18T08:15:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T02:35:02.000Z","uid":219470,"like":17,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0a8cdc6ef135e181b4067e4b5d4a5526b079c00d","tid":2412762,"uid":219470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T08:15:45.000Z","msg":"冚家 GME　冇銀用就要 strong hold<br />\nPapa YO YO YO　繼續 strong hold 冇陰功<br />\n冚家 GME　咁容易 stop loss 氣都嘥<br />\nPapa YO YO YO　吖少理阿爸正仆街<br />\n<br />\n你老豆我十零歲就揸Tesla做司機<br />\n個介紹人係我中學時期嘅一條茂利<br />\n佢老豆原來做經紀　佢阿媽幫手做登記<br />\n咁個仔就自然賣埋啲股唔三唔四<br />\n佢真名叫Elon　落到股場四圍撲<br />\n冰茄曲香好似隻雞係咁啄<br />\n我免費吸兩口起初真係好想嘔<br />\n過咗一陣我都唔知點解係咁拍曬手<br />\n小姐你貴姓　我個網名叫DFV<br />\n啲女圍住我嚟 Squeeze 嘢　你都咪話唔勁<br />\n我熱愛睇股　點樣玩股我最熟<br />\n要自我增值　Strong hold 增強性能力"},{"pid":"d99b8aca450645b5bea9730c4b75aa61aeb0e667","tid":2412762,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T08:16:53.000Z","msg":"收撚皮啦 好撚好笑？"},{"pid":"4bfa15f3125394a9201623adf5c67b6b1f321af8","tid":2412762,"uid":219470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d99b8aca450645b5bea9730c4b75aa61aeb0e667","tid":2412762,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T08:16:53.000Z","msg":"收撚皮啦 好撚好笑？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T08:17:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58e019d5361026f1ce169b11230a132eba9444dd","tid":2412762,"uid":237145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T08:18:52.000Z","msg":"唔係呀都OK"},{"pid":"841247b31b830e6ccb0a16b52f81f7151ee8c1c8","tid":2412762,"uid":311002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T08:19:20.000Z","msg":"10/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"464519c0d4e76144f441a0eafe68cac11696364f","tid":2412762,"uid":293470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T08:23:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/